{{Ẓeṛ taynisemt|Ungal}}
[[File:Fragonard, The Reader.jpg|thumb|''[[Tin i t-ɣren]]'' n [[Jean-Honoré Fragonard|Fragonard]], ɣer 1770, yellan di National Gallery of Art, Washington.]]

'''Ungal''' d [[tawsit taseklant]], yettwaɛqalen s [[allas|wullis]] [[Tasugna|asugnan]] ɣezzifen ddeqs-is. Amur ameqqran yettwaǧǧan i usugen yeteffɣed seg kra n tinfaliyin am « D ungal ! » neɣ deg kra n inumak n urbib « aneglan » yetceggɛen ar ufeɣnami n udmawen, n lḥalat neɣ n taddest. 

Ungal, yettwarun s ifyar n [[taseɣrut|tseɣrut]] deg  timiḍi wis 12 uqbel ad yettwaru s [[tasrit|tesrit]] deg tazwara n timiḍi wis 13, yetsbadu daɣen s userken ines ar [[taɣuri|tɣuri]] tamsimant, d umgerrad ɣef [[tamacahut]]  yellan deg taneṣlit d [[Ansay atlay|asɣelyazen atlay]].
